---
title: Carb Smart Beyond Meat® Cheeseburger Soup with Cheddar and Veggies
description: Packed with Beyond Meat®, creamy cheese and veggies, this dish transforms takeout burger deliciousness into a cozy bowl of soup. This one-pot wonder is sure to hit the spot!

